00:00:01,535 --> 00:00:05,289
Languedoc - 12th century

2
00:01:10,135 --> 00:01:12,649
Joseph, my son!
Take your mother and go!

3
00:02:49,175 --> 00:02:51,814
"By order of the Holy Church
of Languedoc,

4
00:02:52,495 --> 00:02:54,565
the Tribunal of the lnquistion

5
