l'm warning you..

59
00:09:29,015 --> 00:09:31,210
they go to bed
when the sun sets

60
00:09:32,855 --> 00:09:34,811
Abdallah, you forgot these

61
00:09:42,055 --> 00:09:44,808
l'll lock you in a dungeon
filled with books!

62
00:10:01,015 --> 00:10:02,004
Finally...

63
00:10:02,255 --> 00:10:03,290
ls Your Highness sick?

64
00:10:03,495 --> 00:10:05,292
Do l have to be sick
to see you?

65
00:10:06,135 --> 00:10:07,124
Let's play

66
00:10:07,455 --> 00:10:09,366
