- l can't sleep

67
00:10:09,935 --> 00:10:12,005
l've been back from the war
for four days

68
00:10:12,735 --> 00:10:13,770
Where were you?

69
00:10:14,135 --> 00:10:14,806
What's wrong?

70
00:10:17,055 --> 00:10:19,364
lt's my sons,
Nasser and Abdallah

71
