75
00:10:29,615 --> 00:10:32,891
What do you want them to be:
thinking men or lackeys?

76
00:10:33,695 --> 00:10:35,492
l've run circles around
the Spaniards

77
00:10:36,015 --> 00:10:38,324
- We're talking about your sons
- You're obsessed!

78
00:10:38,535 --> 00:10:39,809
You're the one who's worried!

79
