lnstead of being
our children's enemies,

96
00:11:26,535 --> 00:11:28,207
let's try to persuade them

97
00:11:28,615 --> 00:11:31,175
Childish soul-searching
pales in comparison

98
00:11:31,895 --> 00:11:33,294
with the reality of Conquest!

99
00:11:34,295 --> 00:11:35,569
Checkmate

100
00:11:36,335 --> 00:11:37,211
All the better!

101
00:11:37,655 --> 00:11:39,486
You see? l'm unbeatable!

102
00:11:39,695 --> 00:11:40,525
Goodnight

103
00:11:40,735 --> 00:11:41,929
Stay and learn to play

104
00:11:42,215 --> 00:11:44,171
