l'll collapse

105
00:11:44,535 --> 00:11:47,208
- You're like Abdallah!
- We both love life!

106
00:12:13,175 --> 00:12:15,086
Don't ... l'm scared

107
00:12:15,455 --> 00:12:18,413
No. We want each other

108
