Every time we meet, l feel

125
00:13:18,095 --> 00:13:19,289
it's going to be the last

126
00:13:20,335 --> 00:13:24,408
The son of the Caliph
and a poor gypsy girl..

127
00:13:31,575 --> 00:13:33,850
