and shout:

146
00:15:22,775 --> 00:15:26,085
"Why pine away for someone
who ignores you?

147
00:15:28,095 --> 00:15:30,928
"Why care for so uncaring
a creature?

148
00:15:31,695 --> 00:15:34,687
"You, prisoner of pride
and vanity"

149
00:15:35,535 --> 00:15:37,446
Such depth in so few words

150
00:15:37,855 --> 00:15:39,083
lt's by Abu Nawas

151
00:15:40,535 --> 00:15:41,411
lt's amazing!

152
00:15:42,135 --> 00:15:44,046
You're so young

153
00:15:44,535 --> 00:15:46,093
and already a genius!

154
00:15:49,055 --> 00:15:50,329
Stay with us a while

155
00:15:50,895 --> 00:15:52,965
Share your learning with us

156
00:15:53,815 --> 00:15:56,488
What does "prisoner of pride"
mean?

157
00:15:59,735 --> 00:16:03,694
lt's sort of what happens
when your heart is sort of...

158
